WEBVTT

00:00:01.014 --> 00:00:02.325
Hammaga salom.

00:00:02.325 --> 00:00:06.473
Siz bilan suhatlashish
men uchun sharaf,

00:00:06.473 --> 00:00:11.680
va bugun men omad va adolat hamda

00:00:11.680 --> 00:00:14.373
ularning aloqadorligini gapirmoqchiman.

00:00:14.373 --> 00:00:15.554
Bir necha yil oldin

00:00:15.554 --> 00:00:18.976
mening sobiq talabam qizi haqida 
gaplashish uchun

00:00:18.976 --> 00:00:21.034
menga qo'ng'iroq qildi.

00:00:21.038 --> 00:00:23.493
Uning litseyning 
yuqori sinfida o'qiydigan qizi

00:00:23.497 --> 00:00:28.541
men ta'lim beradigan 
Svartmor kollejiga hujjat topshirishni

00:00:28.545 --> 00:00:29.871
jin dildan istar ekan,

00:00:29.871 --> 00:00:35.343
u qizi o'qishga kira olish yo kirmasligi 
haqida mening fikrimni bilmoqchi edi.